item.description:
The name is Ziflaj, Aldo Ziflaj (cue the Bond music)&hellip;
I am a Software Engineer @ Leadfeeder working out of Tirana, Albania.
My hobby in computers sparked in 2008, coincidentally during the Financial crisis of 2007-2008. They say coincidences don&rsquo;t really exist and some people are still feeling the consequences of the crisis, so my lawyer advises me to say I am not in any way to accept responsibility about it.
